ENTRY            F0645   20251222   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0645001   20251222   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  8         14
TITLE      Large-angle alpha scattering from 40Ca is not anomalous
AUTHOR     (H.P.Gubler,U.Kiebele,H.O.Meyer,G.R.Plattner,I.Sick)
INSTITUTE  (2SWTBAS)
REFERENCE  (J,PL/B,74,202,1978)
FACILITY   (CYCLO,2SWTBAS)
SAMPLE     The targets were natural Ca of 0.2 - 0.4 mg/cm2
           thickness evaporated onto a thin carbon foil.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-1) Overall normalization uncertainty.
           (ERR-2) The errors include statistical as well as
           systematic contributions except for an overall
           normalization uncertainty.
HISTORY    (20040218C)
           (20251222U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           DATA-ERR1 -> ERR-1; DATA-ERR2 -> ERR-2.
ENDBIB              14
